  <channel>
    <title>Refugees contributor: Malin Björk</title>
    <description>Malin Björk is a member of the European Parliament for the Swedish Left Party and special rapporteur to the parliament on refugee resettlement. The parliament appoints a rapporteur for every proposal for a new E.U. directive launched by the European Commission. Their role is to negotiate and write a report with members of the other political groups. The content of this report is then put to a vote on the parliament floor.
</description>
